{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"prepareForReuse","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The default implementation of this method does nothing. You can override it in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"your custom annotation view implementation to put the view in a known state","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"before it is returned to your map view delegate.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/prepareForReuse"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Called when the view is removed from the reuse queue."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/prepareforreuse"]}],"metadata":{"title":"prepareForReuse","roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(im)prepareForReuse","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"prepareForReuse"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"prepareForReuse","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L117","fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h"}},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"title":"MLNAnnotationView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/prepareForReuse":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"prepareForReuse","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"prepareForReuse"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Called when the view is removed from the reuse queue."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/prepareForReuse","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/prepareforreuse"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","title":"MLNAnnotation"}}}